(19, 13, 1, 'https://www.theverge.com/news/808589/senators-ai-chatbot-bill-age-verification-teen-ban', 'Senators propose banning teens from using AI chatbots', 'A new piece of legislation could require AI companies to verify the ages of everyone who uses their chatbots. Sens. Josh Hawley (R-MO) and Richard Blumenthal (D-CT) introduced the GUARD Act on Tuesday, which would also ban everyone under 18 from accessing AI …', '<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul>\r\nThe new rules would force AI companies to verify whether users are over 18. \r\nThe new rules would force AI companies to verify whether users are over 18. \r\nby\r\nE… [+2611 chars]', 'https://www.theverge.com/news/808589/senators-ai-chatbot-bill-age-verification-teen-ban', 'https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/30f782a9.jpeg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200', '2025-10-29 05:42:04', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"the-verge\",\"name\":\"The Verge\"},\"author\":\"Emma Roth\",\"title\":\"Senators propose banning teens from using AI chatbots\",\"description\":\"A new piece of legislation could require AI companies to verify the ages of everyone who uses their chatbots. Sens. Josh Hawley (R-MO) and Richard Blumenthal (D-CT) introduced the GUARD Act on Tuesday, which would also ban everyone under 18 from accessing AI \\u2026\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theverge.com\\/news\\/808589\\/senators-ai-chatbot-bill-age-verification-teen-ban\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/platform.theverge.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/sites\\/2\\/2025\\/10\\/30f782a9.jpeg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-28T22:42:04Z\",\"content\":\"<ul><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\nThe new rules would force AI companies to verify whether users are over 18. \\r\\nThe new rules would force AI companies to verify whether users are over 18. \\r\\nby\\r\\nE\\u2026 [+2611 chars]\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:17', '2025-1