(22, 15, 1, 'https://www.theverge.com/news/813817/apple-podcasts-automatic-links-and-chapters', 'Apple Podcasts is generating automatic links and chapters', 'Apple Podcasts will soon include automatically-generated chapters for shows in English and allow creators to add links at specific timestamps in their episodes. Timed links may also be added to episodes automatically whenever creators mention another podcast.…', '<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul>\r\nThe new features will arrive in iOS 26.2, which is currently in developer beta testing.\r\nThe new features will arrive in iOS 26.2, which is currently in develope… [+2188 chars]', 'https://www.theverge.com/news/813817/apple-podcasts-automatic-links-and-chapters', 'https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23986636/acastro_STK461_03.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200', '2025-11-05 06:34:28', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"the-verge\",\"name\":\"The Verge\"},\"author\":\"Stevie Bonifield\",\"title\":\"Apple Podcasts is generating automatic links and chapters\",\"description\":\"Apple Podcasts will soon include automatically-generated chapters for shows in English and allow creators to add links at specific timestamps in their episodes. Timed links may also be added to episodes automatically whenever creators mention another podcast.\\u2026\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theverge.com\\/news\\/813817\\/apple-podcasts-automatic-links-and-chapters\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/platform.theverge.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/sites\\/2\\/chorus\\/uploads\\/chorus_asset\\/file\\/23986636\\/acastro_STK461_03.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-11-04T22:34:28Z\",\"content\":\"<ul><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\nThe new features will arrive in iOS 26.2, which is currently in developer beta testing.\\r\\nThe new features will arrive in iOS 26.2, which is curren