(29, 21, 1, 'https://www.npr.org/2025/10/31/g-s1-95763/trump-wikipedia-musk-shein-amazon-frankenstein-news-quiz', 'What has 11 questions and makes you feel smart? Our news quiz!', 'From monsters to politics and (maybe) everything in between, it\'s the weekly news quiz.', 'Boo! Need a last-minute costume? Just print out the quiz, staple it to your clothing, and copy the below score feedback options onto slips of paper. Make trick-or-treaters take the quiz, then give th… [+217 chars]', 'https://www.npr.org/2025/10/31/g-s1-95763/trump-wikipedia-musk-shein-amazon-frankenstein-news-quiz', 'https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2827x1590+0+0/resize/1400/quality/100/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Fbe%2F50428da4482f9108dfe7689a7d1b%2Fhalloween.jpg', '2025-10-31 16:01:00', '{\"source\":{\"id\":null,\"name\":\"NPR\"},\"author\":\"Holly J. Morris\",\"title\":\"What has 11 questions and makes you feel smart? Our news quiz!\",\"description\":\"From monsters to politics and (maybe) everything in between, it\'s the weekly news quiz.\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.npr.org\\/2025\\/10\\/31\\/g-s1-95763\\/trump-wikipedia-musk-shein-amazon-frankenstein-news-quiz\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/npr.brightspotcdn.com\\/dims3\\/default\\/strip\\/false\\/crop\\/2827x1590+0+0\\/resize\\/1400\\/quality\\/100\\/format\\/jpeg\\/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F41%2Fbe%2F50428da4482f9108dfe7689a7d1b%2Fhalloween.jpg\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-31T09:01:00Z\",\"content\":\"Boo! Need a last-minute costume? Just print out the quiz, staple it to your clothing, and copy the below score feedback options onto slips of paper. Make trick-or-treaters take the quiz, then give th\\u2026 [+217 chars]\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:17', '2025-11-10 08:16:33', NULL),
(30, 22, 1, 'https://www.businessinsider.com/publishers-patent-infringement-lawsuits-adtech-rich-media-club-gannett-guardian-2025-10', 'A wave of patent lawsuits is hitting big news publishers, including Gannett and The Guardian', 'Publishers sued by Rich Media Club include Comcast, Guardian Media Group, Gannett, News Corp\'s UK publishing arm, and MediaNews Group.', 'Big publishers are being hit with patent infringement lawsuits over the adtech on their websites.MarioGuti/Getty Images\r\n<ul><li>A group of big publishers has been hit with patent infringement lawsui… [+7189 chars]', 'https://www.businessinsider.com/publishers-patent-infringement-lawsuits-adtech-rich-media-club-gannett-guardian-2025-10', 'https://i.insider.com/68e79013cc993f9955cfda97?width=1200&format=jpeg', '2025-10-15 21:18:29', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"business-insider\",\"name\":\"Business Insider\"},\"author\":\"Lara O\'Reilly\",\"title\":\"A wave of patent lawsuits is hitting big news publishers, including Gannett and The Guardian\",\"description\":\"Publishers sued by Rich Media Club include Comcast, Guardian Media Group, Gannett, News Corp\'s UK publishing arm, and MediaNews Group.\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.businessinsider.com\\/publishers-patent-infringement-lawsuits-adtech-rich-media-club-gannett-guardian-2025-10\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/i.insider.com\\/68e79013cc993f9955cfda97?width=1200&format=jpeg\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-15T14:18:29Z\",\"content\":\"Big publishers are being hit with patent infringement lawsuits over the adtech on their websites.MarioGuti\\/Getty Images\\r\\n<ul><li>A group of big publishers has been hit with patent infringement lawsui\\u2026 [+7189 chars]\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:17', '2025-11-10 08:16:33', NULL),
(31, 23, 1, 'https://www.businessinsider.com/cnn-ceo-mark-thompson-streaming-sale-wbd-peter-kafka-interview-2025-10', 'Why CNN CEO Mark Thompson thinks you\'ll pay $7 a month to stream the news', 'The man behind The New York Times\' digital turnaround is trying to pull off another transformation — this time with CNN\'s new streaming service.', 'CNN CEO Mark Thompson helped the New York Times flip its business model on its head a decade ago. Now he\'s trying to do the same thing with the cable TV network.Dimitrios Kambouris/Getty Images for W… [+7251 chars]', 'https://www.businessinsider.com/cnn-ceo-mark-thompson-streaming-sale-wbd-peter-kafka-interview-2025-10', 'https://i.insider.com/68fff172c007ca8c2737baa9?width=1200&format=jpeg', '2025-10-28 17:00:02', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"business-insider\",\"name\":\"Business Insider\"},\"author\":\"Peter Kafka\",\"title\":\"Why CNN CEO Mark Thompson thinks you\'ll pay $7 a month to stream the news\",\"description\":\"The man behind The New York Times\' digital turnaround is trying to pull off another transformation \\u2014 this time with CNN\'s new streaming service.\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.businessinsider.com\\/cnn-ceo-mark-thompson-streaming-sale-wbd-peter-kafka-interview-2025-10\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/i.insider.com\\/68fff172c007ca8c2737baa9?width=1200&format=jpeg\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-28T10:00:02Z\",\"content\":\"CNN CEO Mark Thompson helped the New York Times flip its business model on its head a decade ago. Now he\'s trying to do the same thing with the cable TV network.Dimitrios Kambouris\\/Getty Images for W\\u2026 [+7251 chars]\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:17', '2025-11-10 08:16:34', NULL),
(32, 23, 1, 'https://www.businessinsider.com/fox-ai-fake-snap-meta-yann-lecun-newsmax-2025-11', 'Now AI fakes are fooling news outlets — and maybe AI pros?', 'We\'ve known for years that AI would be able to make fake video that could dupe us. Now it looks like we\'re here.', 'An apparently AI-generated video of an AI NYPD person talking to AI ICE agents shows how easy it is to be tricked.Screengrab\r\n<ul><li>\"Fake News\" used to be a real news story you didn\'t like.</li><li… [+3438 chars]', 'https://www.businessinsider.com/fox-ai-fake-snap-meta-yann-lecun-newsmax-2025-11', 'https://i.insider.com/69090dad0be9845f2dc59ce8?width=718&format=jpeg', '2025-11-04 04:39:10', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"business-insider\",\"name\":\"Business Insider\"},\"author\":\"Peter Kafka\",\"title\":\"Now AI fakes are fooling news outlets \\u2014\\u00a0and maybe AI pros?\",\"description\":\"We\'ve known for years that AI would be able to make fake video that could dupe us. Now it looks like we\'re here.\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.businessinsider.com\\/fox-ai-fake-snap-meta-yann-lecun-newsmax-2025-11\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/i.insider.com\\/69090dad0be9845f2dc59ce8?width=718&format=jpeg\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-11-03T20:39:10Z\",\"content\":\"An apparently AI-generated video of an AI NYPD person talking to AI ICE agents shows how easy it is to be tricked.Screengrab\\r\\n<ul><li>\\\"Fake News\\\" used to be a real news story you didn\'t like.<\\/li><li\\u2026 [+3438 chars]\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:17', '2025-11-10 08:16:34', NULL),
(33, 26, 1, 'https://www.businessinsider.com/youtube-tv-abc-news-fight-disney-carriage-dispute-2025-11', 'YouTube throws shade at ABC News in the latest chapter of its fight with Disney', 'Disney asked YouTube to add ABC ahead of Election Day. YouTube TV said in the past two elections, its viewers largely did not watch ABC.', 'YouTube said that election news is widely available outside ABC News as well.Thomas Trutschel/Photothek via Getty Images\r\n<ul><li>YouTube took a swipe at Disney when responding to its request to rest… [+3387 chars]', 'https://www.businessinsider.com/youtube-tv-abc-news-fight-disney-carriage-dispute-2025-11', 'https://i.insider.com/69098bbbc007ca8c27382cb2?width=1200&format=jpeg', '2025-11-04 15:09:37', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"business-insider\",\"name\":\"Business Insider\"},\"author\":\"Shubhangi Goel\",\"title\":\"YouTube throws shade at ABC News in the latest chapter of its fight with Disney\",\"description\":\"Disney asked YouTube to add ABC ahead of Election Day. YouTube TV said in the past two elections, its viewers largely did not watch ABC.\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.businessinsider.com\\/youtube-tv-abc-news-fight-disney-carriage-dispute-2025-11\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/i.insider.com\\/69098bbbc007ca8c27382cb2?width=1200&format=jpeg\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-11-04T07:09:37Z\",\"content\":\"YouTube said that election news is widely available outside ABC News as well.Thomas Trutschel\\/Photothek via Getty Images\\r\\n<ul><li>YouTube took a swipe at Disney when responding to its request to rest\\u2026 [+3387 chars]\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:17', '2025-11-10 08:16:34', NULL),
(34, 24, 1, 'https://www.theverge.com/news/798875/california-just-passed-a-new-law-requiring-ai-to-tell-you-its-ai', 'New California law requires AI to tell you it’s AI', 'A bill attempting to regulate the ever-growing industry of companion AI chatbots is now law in California, as of October 13th. California Gov. Gavin Newsom signed into law Senate Bill 243, billed as “first-in-the-nation AI chatbot safeguards” by state senator…', '<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul>\r\nSB 243 institutes new safeguards on AI chatbots.\r\nSB 243 institutes new safeguards on AI chatbots.\r\nby\r\nHayden FieldClose\r\nHayden Field\r\nPosts from this author w… [+3201 chars]', 'https://www.theverge.com/news/798875/california-just-passed-a-new-law-requiring-ai-to-tell-you-its-ai', 'https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/09/STK_414_AI_CHATBOT_R2_CVirginia_D.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200', '2025-10-14 00:13:58', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"the-verge\",\"name\":\"The Verge\"},\"author\":\"Hayden Field, Dominic Preston\",\"title\":\"New California law requires AI to tell you it\\u2019s AI\",\"description\":\"A bill attempting to regulate the ever-growing industry of companion AI chatbots is now law in California, as of October 13th. California Gov. Gavin Newsom signed into law Senate Bill 243, billed as \\u201cfirst-in-the-nation AI chatbot safeguards\\u201d by state senator\\u2026\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theverge.com\\/news\\/798875\\/california-just-passed-a-new-law-requiring-ai-to-tell-you-its-ai\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/platform.theverge.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/sites\\/2\\/2025\\/09\\/STK_414_AI_CHATBOT_R2_CVirginia_D.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-13T17:13:58Z\",\"content\":\"<ul><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\nSB 243 institutes new safeguards on AI chatbots.\\r\\nSB 243 institutes new safeguards on AI chatbots.\\