(52, 27, 1, 'https://www.theverge.com/news/809909/figma-weave-weavy-acquisition-ai-design-canvas', 'Figma’s new app lets you combine multiple AI models and editing tools', 'Figma has acquired Weavy, a creative platform that allows users to link AI models and editing tools together, and use them simultaneously in a single canvas. The platform will now live under its new parent company as “Figma Weave,” according to Figma’s announ…', '<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul>\r\nFigma Weave is a node-based canvas platform that gives creators more control over AI-generated content.\r\nFigma Weave is a node-based canvas platform that gives c… [+2056 chars]', 'https://www.theverge.com/news/809909/figma-weave-weavy-acquisition-ai-design-canvas', 'https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Weavy-4.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C8.0144178489107%2C100%2C83.971164302179&w=1200', '2025-10-30 20:16:47', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"the-verge\",\"name\":\"The Verge\"},\"author\":\"Jess Weatherbed\",\"title\":\"Figma\\u2019s new app lets you combine multiple AI models and editing tools\",\"description\":\"Figma has acquired Weavy, a creative platform that allows users to link AI models and editing tools together, and use them simultaneously in a single canvas. The platform will now live under its new parent company as \\u201cFigma Weave,\\u201d according to Figma\\u2019s announ\\u2026\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theverge.com\\/news\\/809909\\/figma-weave-weavy-acquisition-ai-design-canvas\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/platform.theverge.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/sites\\/2\\/2025\\/10\\/Weavy-4.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C8.0144178489107%2C100%2C83.971164302179&w=1200\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-30T13:16:47Z\",\"content\":\"<ul><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\nFigma Weave is a node-based canvas platform that gives creators more control over AI-generated content.\\r\\nFigma Weave is a node-based canvas platform that gives c\\u2026 [+2056 chars]\"