(53, 27, 1, 'https://www.theverge.com/news/811233/microsoft-windows-11-task-manager-duplicate-bug', 'A bizarre Windows 11 bug duplicates Task Manager instead of closing it', 'If you’re a Windows 11 user who frequently uses the Task Manager tool, you should probably avoid Microsoft’s latest OS update. Reddit users and my colleague Tom Warren are reporting that a bug in the optional Windows 11 KB5067036 update is causing Task Manage…', '<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul>\r\nThe optional October 2025 update can cause multiple Task Manager instances to run in the background.\r\nThe optional October 2025 update can cause multiple Task Ma… [+2551 chars]', 'https://www.theverge.com/news/811233/microsoft-windows-11-task-manager-duplicate-bug', 'https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Windows-11-update-task-manager-bug.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200', '2025-10-31 17:37:10', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"the-verge\",\"name\":\"The Verge\"},\"author\":\"Jess Weatherbed\",\"title\":\"A bizarre Windows 11 bug duplicates Task Manager instead of closing it\",\"description\":\"If you\\u2019re a Windows 11 user who frequently uses the Task Manager tool, you should probably avoid Microsoft\\u2019s latest OS update. Reddit users and my colleague Tom Warren are reporting that a bug in the optional Windows 11 KB5067036 update is causing Task Manage\\u2026\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theverge.com\\/news\\/811233\\/microsoft-windows-11-task-manager-duplicate-bug\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/platform.theverge.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/sites\\/2\\/2025\\/10\\/Windows-11-update-task-manager-bug.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-31T10:37:10Z\",\"content\":\"<ul><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\nThe optional October 2025 update can cause multiple Task Manager instances to run in the background.\\r\\nThe optional October 2025 update ca