(79, 38, 1, 'https://www.theverge.com/tech/798901/google-will-let-you-hide-sponsored-results-in-search-after-youve-seen-them', 'Google will let you hide sponsored results in search — after you’ve seen them', 'Ads in Google search results are getting a more prominent label, and a way to hide them if you’re not interested. Handy! The thing is, you still have to look at them first. Currently, Google labels paid results on search pages individually with a “sponsored” …', '<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul>\r\nAds in your search results might be a little less annoying now.\r\nAds in your search results might be a little less annoying now.\r\nby\r\nAllison JohnsonClose\r\nAllis… [+2274 chars]', 'https://www.theverge.com/tech/798901/google-will-let-you-hide-sponsored-results-in-search-after-youve-seen-them', 'https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/STK093_Google_04.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200', '2025-10-14 02:21:38', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"the-verge\",\"name\":\"The Verge\"},\"author\":\"Allison Johnson\",\"title\":\"Google will let you hide sponsored results in search \\u2014 after you\\u2019ve seen them\",\"description\":\"Ads in Google search results are getting a more prominent label, and a way to hide them if you\\u2019re not interested. Handy! The thing is, you still have to look at them first. Currently, Google labels paid results on search pages individually with a \\u201csponsored\\u201d \\u2026\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theverge.com\\/tech\\/798901\\/google-will-let-you-hide-sponsored-results-in-search-after-youve-seen-them\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/platform.theverge.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/sites\\/2\\/2025\\/02\\/STK093_Google_04.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.732984293194%2C100%2C78.534031413613&w=1200\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-13T19:21:38Z\",\"content\":\"<ul><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\nAds in your search results might be a little less annoying