(84, 13, 1, 'https://www.theverge.com/news/805261/netflix-stranger-things-5-finale-theaters', 'The Stranger Things series finale is coming to theaters', 'Netflix is bringing the Stranger Things series finale to theaters. The show’s final episode will hit theaters at the same time it premieres on the streaming service on December 31st at 8PM ET. It’ll be available in more than 350 theaters across the US and Can…', '<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul>\r\nThe two-hour-long episode will debut in more than 350 theaters across North America.\r\nThe two-hour-long episode will debut in more than 350 theaters across North… [+2318 chars]', 'https://www.theverge.com/news/805261/netflix-stranger-things-5-finale-theaters', 'https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/stranger-things-5-screenshot.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=2.4091666666667,0,95.181666666667,100', '2025-10-23 20:44:35', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"the-verge\",\"name\":\"The Verge\"},\"author\":\"Emma Roth\",\"title\":\"The Stranger Things series finale is coming to theaters\",\"description\":\"Netflix is bringing the Stranger Things series finale to theaters. The show\\u2019s final episode will hit theaters at the same time it premieres on the streaming service on December 31st at 8PM ET. It\\u2019ll be available in more than 350 theaters across the US and Can\\u2026\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theverge.com\\/news\\/805261\\/netflix-stranger-things-5-finale-theaters\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/platform.theverge.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/sites\\/2\\/2025\\/10\\/stranger-things-5-screenshot.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=2.4091666666667,0,95.181666666667,100\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-23T13:44:35Z\",\"content\":\"<ul><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\nThe two-hour-long episode will debut in more than 350 theaters across North America.\\r\\nThe two-hour-long episode will debut in more than 350 theaters across North\\u2026 [+2318 chars]\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:17', '2025-11-10 08:16: