(85, 32, 1, 'https://www.theverge.com/news/806926/oneplus-15-launch-china-specs-camera-battery', 'OnePlus 15 arrives in China, global launch ‘coming soon’', 'After a steady stream of spec teases, OnePlus has launched its new OnePlus 15 flagship in China today. Release plans elsewhere are still unconfirmed, but the company promises that the phone’s global launching will be “soon.” We’ve known what the 15 would look…', '<ul><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul>\r\nIt brings a fast 165Hz refresh rate and huge 7,300mAh battery.\r\nIt brings a fast 165Hz refresh rate and huge 7,300mAh battery.\r\nby\r\nDominic PrestonClose\r\nDominic… [+2510 chars]', 'https://www.theverge.com/news/806926/oneplus-15-launch-china-specs-camera-battery', 'https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/09/oneplus-15-sand-storm-back.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.752607989199%2C100%2C78.494784021602&w=1200', '2025-10-27 20:24:55', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"the-verge\",\"name\":\"The Verge\"},\"author\":\"Dominic Preston\",\"title\":\"OnePlus 15 arrives in China, global launch \\u2018coming soon\\u2019\",\"description\":\"After a steady stream of spec teases, OnePlus has launched its new OnePlus 15 flagship in China today. Release plans elsewhere are still unconfirmed, but the company promises that the phone\\u2019s global launching will be \\u201csoon.\\u201d We\\u2019ve known what the 15 would look\\u2026\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theverge.com\\/news\\/806926\\/oneplus-15-launch-china-specs-camera-battery\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/platform.theverge.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/sites\\/2\\/2025\\/09\\/oneplus-15-sand-storm-back.jpg?quality=90&strip=all&crop=0%2C10.752607989199%2C100%2C78.494784021602&w=1200\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-10-27T13:24:55Z\",\"content\":\"<ul><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><li><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\nIt brings a fast 165Hz refresh rate and huge 7,300mAh battery.\\r\\nIt brings a fast 165Hz refresh rate and huge 7,300mAh battery.\\r\\nby\\r\\nDominic PrestonClose