(96, 41, 1, 'https://www.businessinsider.com/sprouts-farmers-market-visit-fast-growing-price-competitive-grocery-chain-2025-10', 'I went to Sprouts Farmers Market. The chain is growing fast, and that might be bad news for Whole Foods.', 'Sprouts Farmers Market is opening dozens of new stores. Its selection at a small-format store isn\'t quite Whole Foods, but its prices rival the chain.', 'There\'s a health-focused grocery chain that\'s opening dozens of new locations and it\'s not Whole Foods.\r\nPhoenix-based Sprouts Farmers Market plans to open 37 new stores by the end of the year. The c… [+7087 chars]', 'https://www.businessinsider.com/sprouts-farmers-market-visit-fast-growing-price-competitive-grocery-chain-2025-10', 'https://i.insider.com/6904b7d5599d46a4ccc1371b?width=1200&format=jpeg', '2025-11-02 04:56:01', '{\"source\":{\"id\":\"business-insider\",\"name\":\"Business Insider\"},\"author\":\"abitter@businessinsider.com (Alex Bitter)\",\"title\":\"I went to Sprouts Farmers Market. The chain is growing fast, and that might be bad news for Whole Foods.\",\"description\":\"Sprouts Farmers Market is opening dozens of new stores. Its selection at a small-format store isn\'t quite Whole Foods, but its prices rival the chain.\",\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/www.businessinsider.com\\/sprouts-farmers-market-visit-fast-growing-price-competitive-grocery-chain-2025-10\",\"urlToImage\":\"https:\\/\\/i.insider.com\\/6904b7d5599d46a4ccc1371b?width=1200&format=jpeg\",\"publishedAt\":\"2025-11-01T21:56:01Z\",\"content\":\"There\'s a health-focused grocery chain that\'s opening dozens of new locations and it\'s not Whole Foods.\\r\\nPhoenix-based Sprouts Farmers Market plans to open 37 new stores by the end of the year. The c\\u2026 [+7087 chars]\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:17', '2025-11-10 08:16:34', NULL),
