ott <strong>This season<\\/strong> G5 Y26 R1 5.4 cards\\/game<\\/p>    <h2><strong>Tottenham<\\/strong><\\/h2> <p><strong>Subs from<\\/strong> Kinsky, Austin, Danso, Udogie, Byfield, Hardy, Williams-Barnett, Olusesi, Johnson, Kolo Muani, Tel, Odobert, Scarlett, Thompson<\\/p> <aside class=\\\"element element-rich-link element--thumbnail\\\"> <p> <span>Related: <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.theguardian.com\\/football\\/2025\\/nov\\/07\\/premier-league-10-things-to-look-out-for-this-weekend\\\">Premier League: 10 things to look out for this weekend<\\/a> <\\/p> <\\/aside>  <p><strong>Doubtful<\\/strong> Kudus (knock)<\\/p> <p><strong>Injured<\\/strong> Bissouma (ankle, unknown), Gray (calf, unknown), Takai (thigh, 23 Nov), Solanke (ankle, 23 Nov), Davies (hamstring, unknown), Kulusevski (knee, unknown), Dragusin (knee, unknown), Maddison (knee, unknown)<\\/p> <p>Bergvall (head, 23 Nov)<\\/p> <p><strong>Suspended<\\/strong> None<\\/p> <p><strong>Form<\\/strong> DDWLWL <strong>Leading scorer<\\/strong> Richarlison, Van de Ven 3<\\/p> <h2><strong>Manchester Utd<\\/strong><\\/h2> <p><strong>Subs from<\\/strong> Fredericson, Mee, Heaton, Zirkzee, Heaven, Obi, Maguire, Mount, Mainoo, Ugarte, Bayindir, Dorgu, Mount, Maguire<\\/p> <p><strong>Doubtful<\\/strong> None<\\/p> <p><strong>Injured<\\/strong> Mart\\u00ednez (match fitness, 23 Nov)<\\/p> <p><strong>Suspended<\\/strong> None<\\/p> <p><strong>Form<\\/strong> WLWWWD <strong>Leading scorer<\\/strong> Mbeumo 4<\\/p> <p>***<\\/p> <h2><strong>EVERTON v FULHAM<\\/strong><\\/h2> <p><strong>Saturday<\\/strong> 3pm <strong>Venue<\\/strong> Hill Dickinson Stadium<\\/p> <p><strong>Referee<\\/strong> Andy Madley <strong>This season<\\/strong> G3 Y9 R0 3.0 cards\\/game<\\/p>    <h2><strong>Everton<\\/strong><\\/h2> <p><strong>Subs from<\\/strong> Travers, King, Coleman, Welch, Aznou, Rohl, Iroegbunam, Alcaraz, McNeil, Barry, Beto<\\/p> <p><strong>Doubtful<\\/strong> None<\\/p> <p><strong>Injured<\\/strong> Branthwaite (hamstr