ague Venue Emirates Stadium Referee Tom Bramall This season G4 Y15 R1 4.0 cards/game Arsenal Subs from Arrizabalaga, Setford, White, Hincapié, Mosquera, Lewis-Skelly, Nørgaard, Merino, Martinelli, Nwaneri, Dowman Doubtful None Injured Jesus (knee, Dec), Ødegaard (knee, unknown), Madueke (knee, unknown), Havertz (knee, unknown) Suspended None Form LWDWWW Leading scorer Gyökeres 3 Crystal Palace Subs from Benítez, Matthews, Clyne, Canvot, Ahamada, Sosa, Hughes, Lerma, Devenny, Nketiah, Uche, Esse, Rak-Sakyi Doubtful None Injured Riad (knee, 1 Nov), Doucouré (knee, unknown) Suspended None Form WDWWLD Leading scorer Mateta 5 *** ASTON VILLA v MANCHESTER CITY Sunday 2pm Sky Sports Main Event Venue Villa Park Referee Michael Oliver This season G7 Y16 R1 2.43 cards/game Aston Villa Subs from Martínez, Proctor, Lindelöf, Mings, Bogarde, Maatsen, Tielemans, Elliott, Barkley, Buendía, Guessand, Sancho Doubtful Digne (ankle), Tielemans (calf) Injured García (knock, unknown) Suspended None Form LDDWWW Leading scorers Buendía, Malen 2 Manchester City Subs from Ortega, Trafford, Bettinelli, Lewis, Aké, Aït-Nouri, O’Reilly, González, Cherki, Marmoush, Bobb, Savinho Doubtful González (fitness) Injured Rodri (hamstring, 2 Nov), Khusanov (unknown, 2 Nov) Suspended None Form LWDWWW Leading scorer Haaland 11 *** WOLVES v BURNLEY Sunday 2pm Sky Sports Mix Venue Molineux Referee Peter Bankes This season G6 Y28 R2 5.0 cards/game Wolves Subs from Sá, Bentley, Doherty, T Gomes, Agbadou, Møller Wolfe, Tchatchoua, Bellegarde, Arokodare, Hwang, López, Chirewa Doubtful None Injured Chiwome (knee, unknown) Suspended None Form LLLDDL Leading scorers Bueno, R Gomes, Hwang, Krejci 1 Burnley Subs from Hladky, Weiss, Sonne, Tuanzebe, Delcroix, Worrall, Humphreys, Pires, Laurent, Mejbri, Edwards, Trésor, Broja, Barnes, Tchaouna, Banel, Flemming, Agyei Doubtful Foster (leg) Injured Beyer (hamstring, unknown), Roberts (achilles, unknown), Amdouni (knee, unknown) Suspended None Form LLDLLW Leading scorer