rystal Palace on Sunday\",\"byline\":\"Guardian sport\",\"main\":\"<figure class=\\\"element element-image\\\" data-media-id=\\\"3e7842f306b54ac4de54cafc84616d0db93fc76b\\\"> <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/3e7842f306b54ac4de54cafc84616d0db93fc76b\\/200_0_1658_1326\\/1000.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Erling Haaland and Phil Foden joke in training.\\\" width=\\\"1000\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" class=\\\"gu-image\\\" \\/> <figcaption> <span class=\\\"element-image__caption\\\">Erling Haaland and Phil Foden are expected to start for Manchester City at Aston Villa.<\\/span> <span class=\\\"element-image__credit\\\">Photograph: Martin Rickett\\/PA<\\/span> <\\/figcaption> <\\/figure>\",\"body\":\"<h2><strong>CHELSEA v SUNDERLAND<\\/strong><\\/h2> <p><strong>Saturday<\\/strong> 3pm <strong>Venue<\\/strong> Stamford Bridge<\\/p> <p><strong>Referee<\\/strong> Andy Madley <strong>This season<\\/strong> G1 Y5 R0 5.0 cards\\/game<\\/p>    <h2><strong>Chelsea<\\/strong><\\/h2> <p><strong>Subs from<\\/strong> Slonina, J\\u00f6rgensen, Hato, Adarabioyo, Fofana, Lavia, Santos, Buonanotte, Est\\u00eav\\u00e3o, George, Mheuka, Garnacho, Walsh<\\/p> <p><strong>Doubtful<\\/strong> None<\\/p> <p><strong>Injured<\\/strong> Delap (hamstring, 1 Nov), Palmer (groin, 3 Dec), Badiashile (muscle, 3 Dec), Colwill (knee, unknown), Essugo (thigh, unknown)<\\/p> <p><strong>Suspended<\\/strong> Gusto (one match), Mudryk (indefinite)<\\/p> <p><strong>Form<\\/strong> WDLLWW <strong>Leading scorers<\\/strong> Caicedo, Fern\\u00e1ndez 3<\\/p> <h2><strong>Sunderland<\\/strong><\\/h2> <p><strong>Subs from<\\/strong> Patterson, Geertruida, Masuaku, Neil, O\\u2019Nien, Traor\\u00e9, Brobbey, Adingra, Mayenda<\\/p> <p><strong>Doubtful<\\/strong> Sadiki (ankle)<\\/p> <p><strong>Injured<\\/strong> Alderete (concussion, 3 Nov), Cirkin (wrist, 3 Nov), Mundle (hamstring, 22 Nov), Diarra (groin, Dec)<\\/p> <p><strong>Suspended<\\/strong> None<\\/p> <p><strong>Form<\\/strong> WDDWLW <strong>Leading scorer<\\/strong> I