ubs from S\\u00e1, Bentley, Doherty, T Gomes, Agbadou, Mosquera, Hoever, M\\u00f8ller Wolfe, Bellegarde, Arokodare, R Gomes, L\\u00f3pez, Chirewa, Gonz\\u00e1lez, Chiwome Doubtful Bellegarde (illness), Hwang (knock), Strand Larsen (achilles) Injured None Suspended None Form LLLLDD Leading scorer Bueno, R Gomes, Hwang, Krejci 1 *** FULHAM v ARSENAL Saturday 5.30pm Sky Sports Premier League Venue Craven Cottage Referee Anthony Taylor This season G6 Y18 R0 3.0 cards\\/game Fulham Subs from Lecomte, Cuenca, Reed, Smith Rowe, Jim\\u00e9nez, Kevin, Traor\\u00e9, Kusi-Asare Doubtful Jim\\u00e9nez (hip) Injured Tete (knee, 25 Oct), Chukwueze (calf, 25 Oct), Lukic (groin, Nov), Muniz (hamstring, Nov), Robinson (knee, unknown) Suspended None Form DLWWLL Leading scorer Iwobi, Jim\\u00e9nez, Muniz, Sessegnon, Smith Rowe, Wilson 1 Arsenal Subs from Kepa, Setford, Mosquera, White, Lewis-Skelly, Hincapi\\u00e9, N\\u00f8rgaard, Merino, Nwaneri, Trossard, Dowman Doubtful None Injured Madueke (knee, Nov), \\u00d8degaard (knee, Dec), Jesus (knee, unknown), Havertz (knee, unknown) Suspended None Form WLWDWW Leading scorer Gy\\u00f6keres 3 *** TOTTENHAM v ASTON VILLA Sunday 2pm Sky Sports Premier League Venue Tottenham Hotspur Stadium Referee Simon Hooper This season G6 Y31 R2 5.5 cards\\/game Tottenham Subs from Kinsky, Austin, Danso, Spence, Takai, Davies, Sarr, Gray, Bentancur, Richarlison, Johnson, Kolo Muani Doubtful Davies (muscle), Takai (foot) Injured Kulusevski (knee, Dec), Solanke (ankle, unknown), Dragusin (ACL, unknown), Bissouma (ankle, unknown), Maddison (ACL, unknown) Suspended None Form WLWDDW Leading scorer Richarlison 3 Aston Villa Subs from Bizot, Proctor, Garc\\u00eda, Lindel\\u00f6f, Mings, Maatsen, Onana, Tielemans, Elliott, Barkley, Buend\\u00eda, Guessand, Sancho Doubtful Mings (match fitness), Tielemans (calf) Injured None Suspended None Form LLDDWW Leading scorer Malen 2 *** LIVERPOOL v MANCHESTER UTD Sunday 4.30pm Sky Sports Premier League Venue Anfield Refere