NEWCASTLE v ARSENAL Sunday 4.30pm Sky Sports Premier League Venue St James\\u2019 Park Referee Jarred Gillett This season G3 Y6 R1 2.33 cards\\/game Newcastle Subs from Ramsdale, Krafth, Lascelles, Trippier, Miley, Willock, Elanga, J Murphy, Barnes, Osula Doubtful None Injured Sch\\u00e4r (concussion, 5 Oct), Wissa (knee, 25 Oct), Ramsey (groin, 25 Oct) Suspended None Form DLDWD Leading scorer Guimar\\u00e3es, Osula, Woltemade 1 Arsenal Subs from Kepa, Setford, Mosquera, White, Lewis-Skelly, N\\u00f8rgaard, Merino, Martinelli, Nwaneri, Trossard, Dowman Doubtful None Injured Hincapi\\u00e9 (groin, 4 Oct), Madueke (knee, 1 Nov), Jesus (knee, 30 Dec), Havertz (knee, unknown) Suspended None Form WWLWD Leading scorer Gy\\u00f6keres 3 *** EVERTON v WEST HAM Monday 8pm Sky Sports Premier League Venue Hill Dickinson Stadium Referee Sam Barrott This season G3 Y15 R1 5.33 cards\\/game Everton Subs from Travers, Tyrer, Coleman, Welch, Aznou, Iroegbunam, McNeil, Alcaraz, Dibling, Barry Doubtful None Injured Branthwaite (hamstring, unknown), Patterson (hernia, unknown), R\\u00f6hl (groin, unknown) Suspended None Form LWWDL Leading scorer Ndiaye 2 West Ham Subs from Areola, Fabianski, Wan-Bissaka, Scarles, Todibo, Orford, Potts, Irving, Earthy, Rodr\\u00edguez, Magassa, Marshall, F\\u00fcllkrug, Guilherme Doubtful Wan-Bissaka (muscle) Injured None Suspended Soucek (second of three) Form LLWLL Leading scorer Bowen, Paquet\\u00e1 2\",\"charCount\":\"7293\",\"shouldHideReaderRevenue\":\"false\",\"showAffiliateLinks\":\"false\",\"bylineHtml\":\"<a href=\\\"profile\\/guardian-sport\\\">Guardian sport<\\/a>\",\"showTableOfContents\":\"false\"},\"isHosted\":false,\"pillarId\":\"pillar\\/sport\",\"pillarName\":\"Sport\"}', '2025-11-10 01:15:26', '2025-11-10 01:15:26', NULL);
