(124, NULL, NULL, 'lifeandstyle/2025/oct/09/guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-218', 'Thursday news quiz: book bans, bonkbuster authors and a papal visit', 'Test yourself on topical news trivia, pop culture and general knowledge every Thursday. How will you fare?', 'Thursday rolls around and brings with it another opportunity for you to test your mettle in our weekly quiz. Have you been paying attention to the news – especially the quirkier bits? Find out here, while also enduring a series of tedious in-jokes, and then post your score in the comments to let us know how you got on. Allons-y! The Thursday news quiz, No 218 If you really do think there has been an egregious error in one of the questions or answers – and can show your working and are absolutely 100% positive you aren’t attempting to factcheck a joke – you can complain about it in the comments below. Why not watch Honey, Do You See Me? by EERA instead?', 'https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2025/oct/09/guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-218', 'https://media.guim.co.uk/a8fdcf6b655856f2f5ff0aa602c96b5391f44441/1325_859_1526_1221/500.jpg', '2025-10-09 17:00:22', '{\"id\":\"lifeandstyle\\/2025\\/oct\\/09\\/guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-218\",\"type\":\"article\",\"sectionId\":\"lifeandstyle\",\"sectionName\":\"Life and style\",\"webPublicationDate\":\"2025-10-09T10:00:22Z\",\"webTitle\":\"Thursday news quiz: book bans, bonkbuster authors and a papal visit\",\"webUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theguardian.com\\/lifeandstyle\\/2025\\/oct\\/09\\/guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-218\",\"apiUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/content.guardianapis.com\\/lifeandstyle\\/2025\\/oct\\/09\\/guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-218\",\"fields\":{\"headline\":\"Thursday news quiz: book bans, bonkbuster authors and a papal visit\",\"standfirst\":\"<p>Test yourself on topical news trivia, pop culture and general knowledge every Thursday. How will you fare?<\\/p>\",\"trailText\":\"Test yourself on topical news trivia, pop culture and general knowledge every Thursday. How will you fare?\",\"byline\":\"Martin Belam\",\"main\":\"<figure class=\\\"element element-image\\\" data-media-id=\\\"a8fdcf6b655856f2f5ff0aa602c96b5391f44441\\\"> \\n <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/a8fdcf6b655856f2f5ff0aa602c96b5391f44441\\/1325_859_1526_1221\\/1000.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Pope Leo at the Vatican\\\" width=\\\"1000\\\" height=\\\"800\\\" class=\\\"gu-image\\\"> \\n <figcaption> <span class=\\\"element-image__caption\\\">Pope Leo XIV has been in the news \\u2013 where is he going to make his first overseas visit?<\\/span> <span class=\\\"element-image__credit\\\">Photograph: Andreas Solaro\\/AFP\\/Getty<\\/span> \\n <\\/figcaption> \\n<\\/figure>\",\"body\":\"<p>Thursday rolls around and brings with it another opportunity for you to test your mettle in our weekly quiz. Have you been paying attention to the news \\u2013 especially the quirkier bits? Find out here, while also enduring a series of tedious in-jokes, and then post your score in the comments to let us know how you got on. <em>Allons-y<\\/em>!<\\/p> \\n<p><strong>The Thursday news quiz, No 218<\\/strong><\\/p> \\n<figure class=\\\"element element-atom\\\"> <gu-atom data-atom-id=\\\"28d5e9a2-a33c-45b7-a8e4-292b9fcb59f7\\\" data-atom-type=\\\"quiz\\\"> \\n  <div>\\n   <div class=\\\"quiz\\\" data-questions-length=\\\"15\\\" data-title=\\\"MB Thu new quiz 218 \\u2013&nbsp;9\\/10\\/25\\\">\\n    <ol class=\\\"quiz__questions\\\">\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Canterbury cathedral is getting its first female archbishop. Who?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/517d511f245ac713090a6e11031d05d616208827\\/35_0_3841_3072\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Canterbury cathedral\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Canterbury cathedral is getting its first female archbishop. Who?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Ella Connelly\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Ella Connelly<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Sarah Mullally\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Sarah Mullally<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Fiona Bellamy\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Fiona Bellamy<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Grace Holloway\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Grace Holloway<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Pope Leo has announced his first overseas tour. Where is the pontiff heading?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/10f72e8ea6c568e797d96ffc43417dc9edef46cf\\/0_0_2607_2087\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"The Pope\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Pope Leo has announced his first overseas tour. Where is the pontiff heading?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Egypt and Libya\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Egypt and Libya<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Greece and Cyprus\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Greece and Cyprus<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Turkey and Lebanon\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Turkey and Lebanon<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Syldavia and Borduria\\n\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Syldavia and Borduria <\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Amazon Prime has changed promotional images on its streaming video service after people complained it was doing what \\u2026\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/1d3f16c4816a230b5375b6a77b2030a91bfb2e1d\\/2022_305_1594_1275\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Television\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Amazon Prime has changed promotional images on its streaming video service after people complained it was doing what \\u2026<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Depicting Sherlock Holmes without his pipe\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Depicting Sherlock Holmes without his pipe<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Depicting Indiana Jones without his whip\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Depicting Indiana Jones without his whip<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Depicting James Bond without his gun\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Depicting James Bond without his gun<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Depicting Ron from Sparks without his moustache\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Depicting Ron from Sparks without his moustache<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Hilariously, the first Thursday quiz after the hiatus asked who France\'s new prime minister was, and just four weeks later they have already been yeeted through the door marked \'do one\'. Which French PM has just quit, giving Emmanuel Macron yet another headache?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/d2f86d6d836a281c143122795b9bc91fc4c3b2b0\\/391_1187_2177_1741\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Emmanuel Macron\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Hilariously, the first Thursday quiz after the hiatus asked who France\'s new prime minister was, and just four weeks later they have already been yeeted through the door marked \'do one\'. Which French PM has just quit, giving Emmanuel Macron yet another headache?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"S\\u00e9bastien Lecornu\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">S\\u00e9bastien Lecornu<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"G\\u00e9rald Darmanin\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">G\\u00e9rald Darmanin<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Fran\\u00e7ois Bayrou\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Fran\\u00e7ois Bayrou<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"L\\u00e9on Colbert\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">L\\u00e9on Colbert<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"We lost Jilly Cooper, famous for her \'bonkbuster\' romance novels. Which of these two very famous ones came first?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/3cc4d6f79b889ce1ea8cfd0bac63add9b8dc9c77\\/321_0_4922_3937\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Jilly Cooper\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">We lost Jilly Cooper, famous for her \'bonkbuster\' romance novels. Which of these two very famous ones came first?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"2\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Rivals\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Rivals<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Riders\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Riders<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Talking of books, PEN America\\u2019s Banned in the USA study found what was the most banned book in the 2024-25 school year in the US?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/76c4b7c9b83b354b68cb2cc213d4471535f15e37\\/0_470_2912_2330\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Books\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Talking of books, PEN America\\u2019s Banned in the USA study found what was the most banned book in the 2024-25 school year in the US?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Judy Blume\\u2019s Forever\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Judy Blume\\u2019s Forever<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Anthony Burgess\\u2019s A Clockwork Orange\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Anthony Burgess\\u2019s A Clockwork Orange<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Stephen King\'s Carrie\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Stephen King\'s Carrie<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Gary Barlow\'s Massive Son\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Gary Barlow\'s Massive Son<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"At the Conservative party conference, the Tories managed to give out a free gift where the word \'Britain\' was spelt wrong. What was the gift?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/7fb030f0040e665a6eaba2b7fc3bfee57152a57c\\/2480_483_1007_805\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Clown\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">At the Conservative party conference, the Tories managed to give out a free gift where the word \'Britain\' was spelt wrong. What was the gift?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"A chocolate bar\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">A chocolate bar<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"A small jar of honey\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">A small jar of honey<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"A branded bottle of water\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">A branded bottle of water<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"A very naughty miniature dachshund\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">A very naughty miniature dachshund<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"This is Willow, the official dog of the Guardian Thursday quiz. She wants to know which famous children\'s character is suing the makers of Spitting Image over their recent apparent depiction of it \\u2026\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/e7ff3ca573e2f2e0b4ba19f05d926f1043ec55fa\\/0_351_3024_2419\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Willow, the official dog of the Guardian Thursday quiz\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">This is Willow, the official dog of the Guardian Thursday quiz. She wants to know which famous children\'s character is suing the makers of Spitting Image over their recent apparent depiction of it \\u2026<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Bagpuss\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Bagpuss<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Andy Pandy\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Andy Pandy<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Basil Brush\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Basil Brush<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Paddington\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Paddington<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"This week\'s guest canine is Frank, who the Thursday quiz met down the pub. What a good boy. He wants to know what good cause Drew Scanlon, the man in the Blinking White Guy gif meme, has used his viral fame to raise funds for\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/5cb4a9da1db9ddee200422c55c475bf745cda634\\/0_524_3024_2419\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Frank, a guest dog for the Thursday quiz\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">This week\'s guest canine is Frank, who the Thursday quiz met down the pub. What a good boy. He wants to know what good cause Drew Scanlon, the man in the Blinking White Guy gif meme, has used his viral fame to raise funds for<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"HIV\\/Aids\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">HIV\\/Aids<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Heart disease\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Heart disease<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Cancer\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Cancer<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Multiple sclerosis\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Multiple sclerosis<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Seventeen of David Hockney\'s iPad drawings are to be sold at auction. The drawings are of where?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/069b984bb01