(126, NULL, NULL, 'lifeandstyle/2025/oct/16/the-guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-219', 'Thursday news quiz: French reshuffles, naked cyclists and a heroic dog', 'Test yourself on topical news trivia, pop culture and general knowledge every Thursday. How will you fare?', 'It is Thursday. You’re tired. The quiz is tired. The official dog of the quiz is tired. We’re all tired. But somehow, with the weekend in sight, it is time to summon up the enthusiasm for the only news quiz on the internet that deliberately trolls its readers with increasingly unhinged question themes and in-joke answers – the Guardian’s long-running and slightly baffling Thursday news quiz. There are no prizes but we love to hear how you got on in the comments. Allons-y! The Thursday news quiz, No 219 If you really do think there has been an egregious error in one of the questions or answers – and can show your working and are absolutely 100% positive you aren’t attempting to factcheck a joke – you can complain about it in the comments below. Why not watch Unbroken by Howling Bells instead?', 'https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2025/oct/16/the-guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-219', 'https://media.guim.co.uk/0a89098b115a2861aa0051f2580b694b6de245a2/2004_0_4337_3472/500.jpg', '2025-10-16 17:00:04', '{\"id\":\"lifeandstyle\\/2025\\/oct\\/16\\/the-guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-219\",\"type\":\"article\",\"sectionId\":\"lifeandstyle\",\"sectionName\":\"Life and style\",\"webPublicationDate\":\"2025-10-16T10:00:04Z\",\"webTitle\":\"Thursday news quiz: French reshuffles, naked cyclists and a heroic dog\",\"webUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.theguardian.com\\/lifeandstyle\\/2025\\/oct\\/16\\/the-guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-219\",\"apiUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/content.guardianapis.com\\/lifeandstyle\\/2025\\/oct\\/16\\/the-guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-219\",\"fields\":{\"headline\":\"Thursday news quiz: French reshuffles, naked cyclists and a heroic dog\",\"standfirst\":\"<p>Test yourself on topical news trivia, pop culture and general knowledge every Thursday. How will you fare?<\\/p>\",\"trailText\":\"Test yourself on topical news trivia, pop culture and general knowledge every Thursday. How will you fare?\",\"byline\":\"Martin Belam\",\"main\":\"<figure class=\\\"element element-image\\\" data-media-id=\\\"0a89098b115a2861aa0051f2580b694b6de245a2\\\"> \\n <img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/0a89098b115a2861aa0051f2580b694b6de245a2\\/2004_0_4337_3472\\/1000.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Rhett, a beautiful red and white setter\\\" width=\\\"1000\\\" height=\\\"801\\\" class=\\\"gu-image\\\"> \\n <figcaption> <span class=\\\"element-image__caption\\\">This is Rhett, competing at Crufts in 2017, and he has some questions for you \\u2026<\\/span> <span class=\\\"element-image__credit\\\">Photograph: Teri Pengilley\\/The Guardian<\\/span> \\n <\\/figcaption> \\n<\\/figure>\",\"body\":\"<p>It is Thursday. You\\u2019re tired. The quiz is tired. The official dog of the quiz is tired. We\\u2019re all tired. But somehow, with the weekend in sight, it is time to summon up the enthusiasm for the only news quiz on the internet that deliberately trolls its readers with increasingly unhinged question themes and in-joke answers \\u2013 the Guardian\\u2019s long-running and slightly baffling Thursday news quiz. There are no prizes but we love to hear how you got on in the comments. <em>Allons-y<\\/em>!<\\/p> \\n<p><strong>The Thursday news quiz, No 219<\\/strong><\\/p> \\n<figure class=\\\"element element-atom\\\"> <gu-atom data-atom-id=\\\"688355c8-fd6f-4023-8d61-418e87cf0f81\\\" data-atom-type=\\\"quiz\\\"> \\n  <div>\\n   <div class=\\\"quiz\\\" data-questions-length=\\\"15\\\" data-title=\\\"MB Thu new quiz 219 \\u2013 16\\/10\\/25\\\">\\n    <ol class=\\\"quiz__questions\\\">\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Who won the Nobel prize for literature?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/76c4b7c9b83b354b68cb2cc213d4471535f15e37\\/0_470_2912_2330\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Books\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Who won the Nobel prize for literature?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Boris Jorgen\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Boris Jorgen<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Georgi Gospodinov\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Georgi Gospodinov<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Mircea C\\u0103rt\\u0103rescu\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Mircea C\\u0103rt\\u0103rescu<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"L\\u00e1szl\\u00f3 Krasznahorkai\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">L\\u00e1szl\\u00f3 Krasznahorkai<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"The Thursday quiz cannot believe its luck with French politics at the moment, as for the third time in just six weeks it asks: who has been appointed\\/resigned\\/reappointed as prime minister of France by Emmanuel Macron (pictured)? Come on, you must have clocked his name by now \\u2026\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/d2f86d6d836a281c143122795b9bc91fc4c3b2b0\\/391_1187_2177_1741\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Emmanuel Macron\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">The Thursday quiz cannot believe its luck with French politics at the moment, as for the third time in just six weeks it asks: who has been appointed\\/resigned\\/reappointed as prime minister of France by Emmanuel Macron (pictured)? Come on, you must have clocked his name by now \\u2026<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"G\\u00e9rald Darmanin\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">G\\u00e9rald Darmanin<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"S\\u00e9bastien Lecornu\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">S\\u00e9bastien Lecornu<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Fran\\u00e7ois Bayrou\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Fran\\u00e7ois Bayrou<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"L\\u00e9on Colbert\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">L\\u00e9on Colbert<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Which company is insisting staff hand over their biometric data to access its new Manhattan skyscraper office?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/83c0ec4755494393062f82e1c3397f452fca28d0\\/1055_465_4468_3575\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"A fingerprint\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Which company is insisting staff hand over their biometric data to access its new Manhattan skyscraper office?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Goldman Sachs\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Goldman Sachs<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Morgan Stanley\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Morgan Stanley<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"JP Morgan Chase\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">JP Morgan Chase<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"The Sirius Cybernetics Corporation\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">The Sirius Cybernetics Corporation<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Runners and cyclists are in a tizz because fitness app Strava has got itself into a legal dispute with which  gadget manufacturer?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/f80631d160db7386c2d545b56367bf8b1ecd5096\\/297_94_2322_1858\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Running\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Runners and cyclists are in a tizz because fitness app Strava has got itself into a legal dispute with which gadget manufacturer?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Garmin\\\" data-correct=\\\"true\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Garmin<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Apple\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Apple<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Fitbit\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Fitbit<\\/p><\\/li>\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"Magpie Electricals\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">Magpie Electricals<\\/p><\\/li>\\n      <\\/ol><\\/li>\\n     <li class=\\\"quiz__question question\\\" data-text=\\\"Wales\\u2019s World Cup qualifier defeat by Belgium was interrupted by what?\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/media.guim.co.uk\\/5fdc9546d7085c8a7f96ad9bc172f58e9d0f17c6\\/2366_971_1594_1276\\/500.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Football\\\"><p class=\\\"question__text\\\">Wales\\u2019s World Cup qualifier defeat by Belgium was interrupted by what?<\\/p>\\n      <ol class=\\\"question__answers\\\" type=\\\"A\\\" data-answers-length=\\\"4\\\">\\n       <li class=\\\"question__answer answer\\\" data-text=\\\"A dog getting on to the pitch\\\" data-correct=\\\"false\\\"><p class=\\\"answer__text\\\">A dog getting on to t